criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:
To participate in this study, the patient must meet all of the following inclusion criteria:
1. Confirmed ASD, PFO or PDA and patient characteristics consistent with the corresponding IFU and sizing guidelines;
2. The patient or legally authorized representative has been informed of the nature of the study, agrees to its provisions and has provided written informed consent, approved by the appropriate Ethics Committee (EC);
3. The patient agrees to comply with requirements of the study including the 12 months follow-up.
Exclusion Criteria:
Patients will be excluded if any of the following conditions apply:
1. Any contra-indication mentioned in the corresponding IFU;
2. Currently participating in an investigational drug- or device study.
